OL,3,CLeicester City Council confirms Diwali
OL,4,Ccelebrations to be scaled back
OL,6,FLeicester City Council has confirmed
OL,7,Fthe city's famous Diwali celebrations
OL,8,Fare to be scaled back and combined
OL,9,Finto one annual event, as the
OL,10,Fauthority deals with rising costs.
OL,12,FThis year's celebrations will focus on
OL,13,FDiwali Day itself ` on Thursday 31
OL,14,FOctober ` with an evening of
OL,15,Factivities and entertainment planned
OL,16,Fon Belgrave Road and Cossington Street.
