OL,3,CLeicester City Council confirms Diwali
OL,4,Ccelebrations to be scaled back
OL,6,FThere will not be a separate public
OL,7,Fevent marking the switch-on of the
OL,8,Fcity's Diwali lights this year, though
OL,9,Fthe council says the Golden Mile will
OL,10,Fbe illuminated with 6,000 decorative
OL,11,Flights as usual.
OL,13,FLeicester City Council is combining
OL,14,Fthe events due to the rising costs of
OL,15,Fproviding event and traffic
OL,16,Fmanagement, security, and associated
OL,17,Finfrastructure on two separate days.
OL,18,FThese costs have escalated from
OL,19,F#189,000 in 2018 to almost #250,000
OL,20,Flast year.
