OL,3,CLeicester City Council confirms Diwali
OL,4,Ccelebrations to be scaled back
OL,6,FThe council has worked with the
OL,7,FLeicester Hindu Festival Council
OL,8,F(LHFC) for many years to put on the
OL,9,FDiwali events. Members of the LHFC and
OL,10,Fcommunity representatives were first
OL,11,Fconsulted about the proposed changes
OL,12,Flast summer. It was hoped that a
OL,13,Fcommunity-based fundraising committee
OL,14,Fcould be established to explore
OL,15,Falternative sources of funding or
OL,16,Fsponsorship, but this was unsuccessful.
