OL,3,CLeicester City Council confirms Diwali
OL,4,Ccelebrations to be scaled back
OL,6,FCllr Vi Dempster, Assistant City Mayor
OL,7,Ffor Culture, said: "We're really proud
OL,8,Fof our Diwali celebrations in
OL,9,FLeicester and we want Diwali to
OL,10,Fcontinue to thrive as part of our
OL,11,Fannual events calendar.
OL,13,F"However, the rising cost of providing
OL,14,Factivities on two separate days is now
OL,15,Fentirely unsustainable. We are facing
OL,16,Funprecedented pressures on our budgets
OL,17,Fand the only way we could have
OL,18,Fcontinued with two events is to find
OL,19,Fother ways of securing the substantial
OL,20,Ffunding needed. Unfortunately, that's
OL,21,Fnot happened.
