OL,3,CLeicester City Council confirms Diwali
OL,4,Ccelebrations to be scaled back
OL,6,F"Therefore, following consultation
OL,7,Fwith a number of stakeholders,
OL,8,Fincluding the LHFC and Belgrave
OL,9,FBusiness Association, it has been
OL,10,Fagreed that we will focus on one
OL,11,Fevent, which will be Diwali Day.
OL,13,F"We will of course continue to ensure
OL,14,Fthat the Golden Mile is illuminated
OL,15,Fwith thousands of lamps throughout the
OL,16,Ffestival of Diwali. And we're still
OL,17,Fexpecting to welcome tens of thousands
OL,18,Fof visitors to join us for the
OL,19,Fcelebration."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU{D@MO]
